snippet.title: SlotCarVR - Open BETA trailer
snippet.description:
Slot Car VR - Open BETA now available on Meta Quest

Mixed Reality racing game available for Meta Quest 3, Pro and 2. Build and race tracks around your house. Beat your best lap times and race live with other in your play space or globally online.  

We are looking for users to try out the game and provide feedback via the Slot Car VR discord. https://discord.gg/KEnz8krazy
